      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-fnd-mag-rig-flg    =    "V"
                     go to acc-cod-pro-420
           else if   w-fnd-mag-rig-flg    =    "#"
                     go to acc-cod-pro-440
           else      go to acc-cod-pro-460.
       acc-cod-pro-420.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se prodotto individuato ma gia' spuntato    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "Prodotto gia' controllato!                        
      -              "      "             to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
           go to     acc-cod-pro-100.
       acc-cod-pro-440.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
