      *                  * Preparazione parametri e uscita             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-mag-rig-num    to   w-cnt-slc-num-rig      .
           move      "."                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rig      .
           move      "#"                  to   w-ctl-rig-doc-rpa      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-cod-pro-900.
       acc-cod-pro-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se variazione del valore di default : a re- *
      *                  * impostazione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-mod                not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cod-pro-100.
       acc-cod-pro-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
