      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "pgm/ods/prg/obj/pods3010"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat                                            .
           cancel    s-pat                                            .
