      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-arc-ost-tms    to   w-tes-tip-mps          .
           perform   vis-tip-mps-000      thru vis-tip-mps-999        .
           move      w-fnd-arc-ost-dat    to   w-tes-dat-doc          .
           move      w-fnd-arc-ost-prt    to   w-tes-num-prt          .
